	•	StockRecord

Section 3: Algorithm designs

Check	Exactly what to do
☐	Include a selection of algorithm designs.  ￼
☐	Limit them to up to five complex problems, because the brief says not to show the whole solution and to keep it to several key problems.  ￼
☐	Use flowcharts, pseudocode, or both.

Best algorithms to include:
